<div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12">
  <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Security Policy</h1>

  <div class="prose lg:prose-xl max-w-4xl">
    <p class="mb-4">Last updated: June 1, 2023</p>

    <p class="mb-4">At Genderbase, we prioritize the security of our users and their data. This Security Policy outlines our commitment to protecting the platform and the information entrusted to us.</p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Our Security Practices</h2>

    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mt-6 mb-3">Data Protection</h3>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6">
      <li class="mb-2">All data is encrypted in transit using TLS/SSL protocols</li>
      <li class="mb-2">Sensitive user data is encrypted at rest</li>
      <li class="mb-2">Regular security audits and vulnerability assessments are conducted</li>
      <li class="mb-2">Access to user data is strictly limited and controlled</li>
    </ul>

    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mt-6 mb-3">Authentication and Authorization</h3>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6">
      <li class="mb-2">We implement secure password policies</li>
      <li class="mb-2">Multi-factor authentication is available for all accounts</li>
      <li class="mb-2">Role-based access control limits data access to authorized personnel only</li>
    </ul>

    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mt-6 mb-3">Infrastructure Security</h3>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6">
      <li class="mb-2">Our servers and infrastructure are regularly updated with security patches</li>
      <li class="mb-2">We employ network security measures including firewalls and intrusion detection</li>
      <li class="mb-2">Regular backups are performed to prevent data loss</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Vulnerability Reporting</h2>

    <p class="mb-4">We value the input of security researchers and the broader community in identifying potential vulnerabilities. If you believe you've found a security vulnerability in our systems, we encourage you to report it to us.</p>

    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mt-6 mb-3">How to Report</h3>
    <p class="mb-4">Please send detailed information about potential security issues to:</p>
    <p class="mb-6"><a href="mailto:security@genderbase.org" class="text-primary hover:underline">security@genderbase.org</a></p>

    <p class="mb-4">Include the following in your report:</p>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6">
      <li class="mb-2">Description of the potential vulnerability</li>
      <li class="mb-2">Steps to reproduce the issue</li>
      <li class="mb-2">Any potential impact of the vulnerability</li>
    </ul>

    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mt-6 mb-3">Responsible Disclosure</h3>
    <p class="mb-4">We are committed to:</p>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6">
      <li class="mb-2">Acknowledging receipt of your vulnerability report within 48 hours</li>
      <li class="mb-2">Providing an estimated timeline for addressing the vulnerability</li>
      <li class="mb-2">Notifying you when the vulnerability is fixed</li>
      <li class="mb-2">Recognizing your contribution (if desired) once the vulnerability is addressed</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">User Responsibilities</h2>

    <p class="mb-4">While we work hard to ensure the security of our platform, security is a shared responsibility. We encourage users to:</p>

    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6">
      <li class="mb-2">Use strong, unique passwords for your Genderbase account</li>
      <li class="mb-2">Enable multi-factor authentication when available</li>
      <li class="mb-2">Keep your login credentials confidential</li>
      <li class="mb-2">Sign out from your account when using shared devices</li>
      <li class="mb-2">Report any suspicious activities related to your account</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Security Updates</h2>

    <p class="mb-4">We continually update our security measures to address new threats and vulnerabilities. This security policy may be updated periodically to reflect these changes.</p>

    <div class="mt-8">
      <a href="/privacy" class="btn btn-outline mr-4">Privacy Policy</a>
      <a href="/about" class="btn btn-primary">About Genderbase</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
